Import Embedding¶

Image embedding through deep neural networks.

Signals¶

Inputs:

  • Images

    List of images.

Outputs:

  • Embeddings

    Each image is represented with a vector of numbers.

  • Skipped Images

    Shows list of images, where embeddings were not calculated.

Description¶

Image Embedding reads a list of images and uploads them to a remote server. Remote server uses a deep learning model to calculate a feature vector for each image.
